<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-covid-19-pandemic-is-exposing-the-plague-of-neoliberalism/">The COVID-19 Pandemic Is Exposing the Plague of Neoliberalism</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
